<li><span>$x_{.2} = 110$</span> (total for Tuesday)</li>
<li><span>$x_{.3} = 113$</span> (total for Wednesday)</li>
<li><span>$x_{.4} = 111$</span> (total for Thursday)</li>
<li><span>$x_{.5} = 123$</span> (total for Friday)</li>
<li><span>$n = 5$</span> (5 blocks, as in 5 days of the week)</li>
<li><span>$SS(Tr) = 5 * (4 + 0.64 + 5.76 + 0.16) = 52.8$</span> WTF why is it the same lol lol</li>
<li><span>$SS(Bl) = 4 * (9.3025 + 0.09 + 0.2025 + 0.0025 + 8.7025 = 73.2$</span></li>
<li><span>$SS(E) = $</span> fuck this I'll calculate the total instead</li>
<li><span>$SS(T) = 153.2$</span> so <span>$SS(E) = 153.2 - 126 = 27.2$</span></li>
