<tr>
<td>Low ability in stats</td>
<td>65</td>
<td>40</td>
<td>15</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Avg ""</td>
<td>54</td>
<td>63</td>
<td>29</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>High ""</td>
<td>12</td>
<td>45</td>
<td>27</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>We want to test <span>$H_0:$</span> ability in stats and interest in math are independent and <span>$H_1:$</span> not <span>$H_0$</span>. So what we do first is calculate the row and column sums and write those down in the table margins:</p>
<table class="ui celled padded table">
